msgid "# Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1"
msgstr "# Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 is a state-of-the-art mixture-of-experts (MoE) "
"language model developed by Mistral AI. It features 8 expert models, each "
"with 7B parameters, and is specifically fine-tuned for instruction following"
" tasks."
msgstr ""
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 是由 Mistral AI 开发的最先进的混合专家（MoE）语言模型。它包含 8 "
"个专家模型，每个模型有 7B 参数，并专门针对指令遵循任务进行了微调。"

msgid "Key features of Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 include:"
msgstr "Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 的主要特性包括："

msgid ""
"- 8x7B parameters with sparse activation (only 2 experts activated per token)\n"
"- Strong performance across various NLP tasks\n"
"- Support for extended context length\n"
"- High-quality instruction following capabilities"
msgstr ""
"- 8x7B 参数，稀疏激活（每个 token 仅激活 2 个专家）\n"
"- 在各种 NLP 任务中表现强劲\n"
"- 支持扩展上下文长度\n"
"- 高质量的指令遵循能力"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点部署、精度和性能评估。"

msgid "The `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` model is supported in vllm-ascend."
msgstr "vllm-ascend 支持 `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` 模型。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1`(BF16 version): [Download model weight](https://huggingface.co/mistralai/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1)\n"
"- Quantized versions may be available from third-party providers."
msgstr ""
"- `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1`（BF16 版本）：[下载模型权重](https://huggingface.co/mistralai/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1)\n"
"- 第三方提供商可能提供量化版本。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to a local directory, such as"
" `/data/models/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到本地目录，例如 `/data/models/`。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid ""
"You can use our official docker image to run `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` "
"directly."
msgstr "您可以使用我们的官方 Docker 镜像直接运行 `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1`。"

msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动 Docker 镜像，请参考[使用 Docker](../../installation.md#set-up-"
"using-docker)。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 单节点部署"

msgid ""
"- `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) "
"or 1 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)."
msgstr ""
"- `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` 可以部署在 1 台 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）或 1 台 Atlas "
"800 A2（64G × 8）上。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

msgid ""
"**Notice:**\n"
"The parameters are explained as follows:"
msgstr ""
"**注意：**\n"
"参数说明如下："

msgid ""
"- Setting the environment variable `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING=1` enables balance scheduling. This may help increase output throughput and reduce TPOT in v1 scheduler. However, TTFT may degrade in some scenarios.\n"
"- `--max-model-len` specifies the maximum context length - that is, the sum of input and output tokens for a single request. For testing purposes, a value of `4096` is used here.\n"
"- `--dtype float16` specifies the data type for model weights and computations.\n"
"- `--trust-remote-code` allows loading models with custom code.\n"
"- `--enforce-eager` forces the use of eager execution mode instead of graph compilation, which can be more stable for some models.\n"
"- `--block-size` specifies the block size for KV cache management, with a value of `128` used here.\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` sets the proportion of NPU memory to use for the model, with a value of `0.7` used here to reduce memory usage."
msgstr ""
"- 设置环境变量 `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING=1` 可启用均衡调度。这有助于提高 v1 调度器的输出吞吐量并降低 TPOT。但在某些场景下，TTFT 可能会变差。\n"
"- `--max-model-len` 指定最大上下文长度，即单个请求的输入和输出 token 之和。出于测试目的，此处使用值 `4096`。\n"
"- `--dtype float16` 指定模型权重和计算的数据类型。\n"
"- `--trust-remote-code` 允许加载带有自定义代码的模型。\n"
"- `--enforce-eager` 强制使用即时执行模式而非图编译，这对某些模型可能更稳定。\n"
"- `--block-size` 指定 KV 缓存管理的块大小，此处使用值 `128`。\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` 设置模型使用的 NPU 内存比例，此处使用值 `0.7` 以减少内存占用。"

msgid "## Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 功能验证"

msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with input prompts. "
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 uses a specific prompt format with [INST] and "
"[/INST] tags:"
msgstr ""
"服务器启动后，您可以使用输入提示查询模型。Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 使用带有 [INST] 和 [/INST] "
"标签的特定提示格式："

msgid "For instruction following tasks, you can use prompts like:"
msgstr "对于指令遵循任务，您可以使用如下提示："

msgid "For MoE-related questions:"
msgstr "对于 MoE 相关问题："

msgid ""
"1. Refer to [Using "
"AISBench](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md) for details."
msgstr ""
"1. 详情请参考[使用 AISBench](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md)。"

msgid ""
"2. After execution, you can get the result. For reference, "
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 typically performs well on various benchmarks "
"including reasoning, comprehension, and instruction following tasks."
msgstr ""
"2. 执行后即可获得结果。作为参考，Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 "
"通常在包括推理、理解和指令遵循任务在内的各种基准测试中表现良好。"

msgid "## Performance"
msgstr "## 性能"

msgid "### Using AISBench"
msgstr "### 使用 AISBench"

msgid ""
"Refer to [Using AISBench for performance "
"evaluation](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation) for details."
msgstr ""
"详情请参考[使用 AISBench "
"进行性能评估](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation)。"

msgid "### Using vLLM Benchmark"
msgstr "### 使用 vLLM 基准测试"

msgid ""
"Run performance evaluation of `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` as an example."
msgstr "以 `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` 为例运行性能评估。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [vllm benchmark](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/) for "
"more details."
msgstr "更多详情请参考 [vllm 基准测试](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/benchmarking/)。"

msgid "There are three `vllm bench` subcommands:"
msgstr "`vllm bench` 有三个子命令："

msgid ""
"- `latency`: Benchmark the latency of a single batch of requests.\n"
"- `serve`: Benchmark the online serving throughput.\n"
"- `throughput`: Benchmark offline inference throughput."
msgstr ""
"- `latency`：基准测试单批请求的延迟。\n"
"- `serve`：基准测试在线服务吞吐量。\n"
"- `throughput`：基准测试离线推理吞吐量。"

msgid "Take the `serve` as an example. First, start the server:"
msgstr "以 `serve` 为例。首先，启动服务器："

msgid "## Conclusion"
msgstr "## 结论"

msgid ""
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 is a powerful MoE model that offers excellent "
"performance for instruction following tasks. With proper deployment on "
"Ascend hardware using vllm-ascend, you can achieve high throughput and low "
"latency for your AI applications."
msgstr ""
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 是一个强大的 MoE 模型，为指令遵循任务提供了卓越的性能。通过使用 vllm-ascend "
"在昇腾硬件上进行适当部署，您可以为 AI 应用实现高吞吐量和低延迟。"

msgid ""
"For more details about model capabilities and best practices, refer to the "
"official Mixtral documentation and vllm-ascend user guide."
msgstr "有关模型能力和最佳实践的更多详情，请参考官方 Mixtral 文档和 vllm-ascend 用户指南。"
